Risk Management

| Risk ID | Risk Description                                | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation Strategy                          |
| ------- | ----------------------------------------------- | ---------- | ------ | -------------------------------------------- |
| R1      | Browser local storage limit                     | Medium     | High   | Shift to backend or IndexedDB if data grows  |
| R2      | Incomplete input validation                     | Medium     | Medium | Implement JS validation & alerts             |
| R3      | Mobile responsiveness issues                    | High       | High   | Use flex/grid layouts; test on devices       |
| R4      | Git merge conflicts (solo or team)              | Low        | Medium | Commit regularly, maintain clean branches    |
| R5      | Time constraints in final sprint                | High       | High   | Buffer time in Sprint 4 for polish & testing |
| R6      | Pop-up notification not showing in all browsers | Medium     | Low    | Cross-browser testing                        |

Risk Monitoring Plan
-Weekly Review: Risk review during sprint retrospectives
-Issue Tracker: Log bugs and blockers in Trello/Jira
-Fallback Mechanisms: Optional backup storage options, UI alternatives
